  "body": "### Component\n\nForge, Foundryup\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nSupport setting the foundry version for foundryup in the foundry.toml file.\r\n\r\nThis allows teams and projects to \"pin\" the correct version of foundry that known works with their repository across all CI tools and teammates and helps debugging errors with builds and verification.\r\n\r\nEither a warning can be shown for a wrong version or foundryup can automatically switch to the necessary version similar to how \"engines\" works within package.json or how nvm works in the javascript realm.\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
